<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>١٩٥٥ - حَدِيثٌ <span class="c2">(حم)</span> : “ أَلا إِنَّ الْعَيْشَ عَيْشُ الآخِرَةِ “.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَهُوَ طَرَفٌ مِنَ الْحَدِيثِ الَّذِي قَبْلَهُ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">أَحْمَدُ:</span> ثنا وَكِيعٌ، عَنْ حَمَّادٍ، عَنْهُ، بِهِ.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>